question:
What is the output of the following code snippet?

```java
try {
    int[] arr = new int[5];
    arr[10] = 50;
} catch (ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException e) {
    System.out.print("A");
} catch (Exception e) {
    System.out.print("B");
} finally {
    System.out.print("C");
}
```

